OL,6,FHelen Miller suffered post-traumatic
OL,7,Fstress disorder (PTSD) following a
OL,8,Ftraumatic birth. The 34-year-old from
OL,9,Fthe Wirral, Merseyside, opens up about
OL,10,Fhow flashbacks and a severe lack of
OL,11,Fsleep led her mental health to spiral.
OL,12,FAfter having instrusive thoughts about
OL,13,Fharming her baby, she was hospitalised
OL,14,Ffor three months. Now recovered, she
OL,15,Fruns a support group for women and
OL,16,Ffamilies affected by postnatal
OL,17,Fdepression.
OL,3,C'For months after giving birth, I was
OL,4,Cconvinced my baby wasn't mine'
